author: Epic Games
description:
The award-winning sci-fi city builder is back - remastered, expanded and even more stunning. https://epic.gm/mars-remastered

Colonize Mars and survive the process, from exploration and infrastructure to welcoming colonists and achieving long-term stability. Are you ready? Mars is waiting.
title: Surviving Mars: Relaunched | Available Now

author: Epic Games
description:
Ambrosia Sky: Act One is available to play now! https://epic.gm/ambrosia-sky

You left. Now they’re dead. 
Ambrosia Sky: Act One is an immersive sim about exploring an asteroid colony devastated by a mysterious contamination. Survive and harvest strains of aggressive alien fungi, explore treacherous environments, and find meaning and beauty in so much death.
title: Ambrosia Sky: Act One | Available Now
